Author: jcsxx
Text: I went through cycles for months of being ok for 2 weeks and then everything getting really bad for 2 weeks over and over again and then eventually it became constant and made me wanna die. I hope they take you seriously, you deserve help.

Author: artbang144
Text: Its ok to feel like ur “faking it”. Nothing about ed is truly about the appearance. Remember that weight is just another symptom of the mental illness. Take up journaling or emotion logs. Its going to be ok.
